Cheryl Arutt https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cheryl_Arutt 0 Cheryl Arutt (born May 13, 1966) is a retired American commercial, print, television, and film actress and a clinical and forensic psychologist and media consultant. She co-hosts and is a regular member of the Behavior Bureau on HLN's panel show Dr. Drew On Callâ€‰ and appears as a psychological expert on the Fox News Channel, HLN and In Session.
